title: $:/language/Help/test
description: Run all tests defined in the test edtion

Run the Jasmine test suite defined in the test edition.

```
--test [spec=<spec-filter>] [seed=<seed>]
```

* ''spec'': Optional text to filter which tests to run. Only tests whose name contains the given text will be executed
* ''seed'': Optional random seed for test ordering. If omitted, a random seed is generated automatically

The test runner uses Jasmine with randomised test ordering. The seed used for each run is printed in the output, allowing a specific ordering to be reproduced.

Examples:

* `--test` -- run all tests with a random seed
* `--test seed=38862` -- run all tests with a specific seed for reproducibility
* `--test spec=Widgets` -- run only tests with "Widgets" in their name
